node.text: We are thrilled to finally share the story and inspiration behind our @katemarkerhome textiles and celebrate the official launch of this new line! As I reflect on the process of turning my daughters watercolor motifs into a textile line with the help of my friend @ellishaalexina and my wonderful team, I am hopeful that these fabrics will bring love, joy, and warmth into your home. I can't thank you all enough for your continued support throughout throughout this launch. All textiles are now available to be purchased as pillow covers or fabric by the yard @katemarkerhome. Produced by @margaretrajic and Shot by @courtneycimo

node.text: Making the most out of what’s given is the best outlook to have when it comes to life and decorating small spaces. Using wallpaper helps to draw the eye up and give off the appearance of the space being larger than it truly is. Here’s to making do with what you have! #bestfriendclient😍 #kmidesignstyle | photo: @stofferphotographyinteriors | build: @timbertrailshomes
